WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.920
Ling Ling, have you ever been to the US?

00:03.920 --> 00:08.000
No, I haven't. I've always wanted to go there.

00:08.000 --> 00:11.440
Would you like to come and visit me next year?

00:11.440 --> 00:14.560
That sounds wonderful. I'd love to.

00:14.560 --> 00:19.080
I haven't asked my parents, but I'm sure they'll say yes.

00:19.080 --> 00:21.400
Have you ever traveled by plane?

00:21.400 --> 00:23.600
Yes, I have.

00:23.600 --> 00:25.760
Did you enjoy it?

00:25.760 --> 00:28.800
Yes. It was very exciting,

00:28.800 --> 00:31.080
but I was quite tired.

